code: @Override public void filterProducer(Exchange exchange, WebServiceMessage response) {     for (MessageFilter filter : filters) {         filter.filterProducer(exchange, response).     } }
@Override public void filterConsumer(Exchange exchange, WebServiceMessage response) {     for (MessageFilter filter : filters) {         filter.filterConsumer(exchange, response).     } }
public void setFilters(List<MessageFilter> filters) {     this.filters = filters. }
